name: Do what makes you happy
description:
#8
When I am lost and I don't know what to do whit my life, I ask myself what makes me happy at that exact moment.  It is always a relief, even just to think about it.

Piece #8 of the collection:
I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky art

The series focuses on the fragility of the inner world and brings up topics that we often find in our long journey on earth.
